<h2>🍄 Who We Are</h2>
<p><strong>Mycelium</strong> is a permissionless protocol dedicated to helping people build innovative collaborative relationships through technology, exploring deep insights in blockchain, artificial intelligence, and cutting-edge development.</p>
<p>Our name is inspired by <strong>Mycelium</strong> — an ancient species that has existed on Earth for 4.5 billion years. Mycelium is the underground network that connects everything in nature, transmitting nutrients and information through forests, building the internet of life.</p>
<p><strong>Mycelium means</strong> we follow this 4.5 billion years old species: Mycelium, creating Infra, Protocol and Network for human digital future.</p>
<p>Just as mycelium's role in nature, we are committed to building infrastructure, protocols, and networks for humanity's digital future.</p>

